column5: After all the political crapola threads, I thought some may enjoy a story about one mans struggle to nourish himself with a happy ending!  http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/27228081/?GT1=43001
Hey Glen,  In the article, they forgot to mention the calories the man injested in the 4.39 hour it took him to eat that
I think I'd be more worried about if there was enough T.P. in the house after eating that thing!!!  "Honey! Get the camera... I think this thing still has cheese on it!!!"
You could  call that a suicide attempt. He's gonna be unwell for a few days.
After the way I ate for Thanksgiving weekend, I would have no problem eating that miniscule burger...lol. Prolly do it in less time too.
